trasbg.fr/"{\textgreater}cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr{\textless}/A{\textgreater} (ftp://130.79.128.5) or via {\textless}A href="http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/viz-bin/cat/J/A+A/658/A69"{\textgreater}http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/viz-bin/cat/J/A+A/658/A69{\textless}/A{\textgreater} {\textless}P /{\textgreater}Based on observations collected at the ESO Paranal observatory under ESO program 099.D-0895 and 0101.D-0163.},
